data.title: PacHydro bid is business as usual for IFM
data.meta_description: Taking over Pacific Hydro won't be a major step for Industry Funds Management, writes Barrie Dunstan.
data.text:
Taking over Pacific Hydro won't be a major step for Industry Funds Management, writes Barrie Dunstan.

Garry Weaven, chairman of Industry Funds Management, which is bidding $725 million for Pacific Hydro says: "Yes, there's obviously a certain amount of risk in it, but this is an asset that we know pretty well.
